      "description": "Dependable transportation at a budget-friendly price, this vehicle offers solid everyday utility for the buyer who values affordability and straightforward ownership. An excellent option for commuting, errands, or a backup vehicle, it presents a chance to get on the road for far less than newer alternatives. Priced to reflect its condition while still delivering real-world value, this is a practical buy for someone seeking low-cost motoring.",
