      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with good bones and plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward, honest option for someone who wants dependable basic transport, a project, or a handy runabout without spending a fortune. It has the kind of value that makes sense for a buyer who doesn\u2019t mind a little TLC and wants something budget-friendly. Priced to be fair and appealing, this could be a great fit for the right person.",
