      "description": "Strong-running used car with solid core mechanicals and plenty of life left for the right buyer. The engine pulls cleanly, the transmission does its job, and the chassis feels like a good foundation for a budget commuter, shop car, or weekend project. Cosmetic wear and age-related imperfections are present, but this is the kind of honest driver that still offers dependable point-A-to-B capability. A practical, affordable option for someone who values function, serviceable hardware, and future upside.",
